{"tid":1519045,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[2047前逃生門] [齊上齊落] [一個都不能少] 各位手足請入！","createTime":"2019-08-30T12:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T19:30:36.000Z","uid":61161,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3cd7dd29a59c7144cd4b45c46e8e554a4091d2","tid":1519045,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"抗爭個代價好大，唔忍心再見到有手足受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個Post唔長，希望大家認真睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個idea可以擁有民主同自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有個大限，就係2047年前，否則逃生門會關閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋一齊集中移民去台灣嘅其中一個城市去建立我哋嘅新香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（地點大家再傾，否則大家會去哂英國/加拿大/澳洲etc. 原因下面再講）<br />\n<br />\n香港呢個城市最靚嘅地方唔係高樓大廈，而係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其咁難爭取，不如直接上挪亞方舟，去一個新嘅地方，重身建立我哋嘅香港，到時可以一齊除低哂口罩，同各位義士相擁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n1. 門檻低 （有能力嘅手足可以帶埋能力唔夠嘅手足，最緊要夠錢）<br />\n2. 文化相近<br />\n3. 集中一個地點，同其他香港人一齊生活落去（大家都知道唔少手足過咗去，忍心掉低佢地係台灣咩？）<br />\n4. 帶埋我哋嘅質素、知識、人材、資產過去（我哋唔係難民，我哋嘅示威反映咗我哋嘅人民質素，唔相信台灣會落閘，但2047後唔一定俾門移民海外或台灣）<br />\n5. 教育、醫療水平、法治都有一定嘅國際水平<br />\n6. 唔需要再為咗層樓咁吃力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以住大啲添<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1. 人工低咗（不過生活成本都相應降低）<br />\n2. 放棄咗我哋嘅家鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 未必個個都有能力移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其20/25年做按揭供層樓，倒不如用25年時間，一齊實行呢個計劃，中小學生一樣夠時間去做！<br />\n<br />\n記住我哋嘅口號，一個都不能少、齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實烏克蘭人雖然好慘烈咁贏咗，但往後嘅生活都係比贏之前更加艱難。（聽朋友講）<br />\n<br />\n深藍/廢老友得佢地就係度享受大灣區榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 父母係淺黃/深黃就可以一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel聖域界都可以有新Asgard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係呢個城市嘅子民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係呢個城市嘅景觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係要有共識去搵一個地方！！！<br />\n去開台灣旅行嘅大家有無好提議？！<br />\n唔好散落係唔同城市！！<br />\n最好要住返埋一齊呀！！<br />\n到時係台灣想點遊行集會都得呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將香港變成終極焦土！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9390f73d05b59fa21457c4a21b7d30b588baab7a","tid":1519045,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=ec1afa33\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=851aaf9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=721a425a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"74f2d740f7121c16374e38dcc4121ebb6ad2786c","tid":15